---
// Hero.astro
---

<section class="relative min-h-[70vh] sm:min-h-screen max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 overflow-hidden w-full">
  <!-- Imagen de fondo -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center left-0 sm:left-[40rem]"
    style="background-image: url('/images/childs/1.png');"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 z-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto hidden sm:block">
    <img
      src="/images/decore-1.png"
      alt="Onda"
      class="w-full h-[12rem] object-cover"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-[32rem] z-20 mx-auto hidden lg:block">
    <img
      src="/images/decore-2.png"
      alt="Onda"
      class="w-full h-[9rem] object-cover"
    />
  </div>

  <!-- Degradado blanco -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-white/100 to-transparent"
  >
  </div>

  <!-- Contenido -->
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-2xl px-6 pb-10 sm:pb-24 pt-20 sm:pt-32">
    <div class="flex items-end justify-between mb-4">
      <img
        src="/images/butterfly.png"
        alt="Mariposa"
        class="w-24 sm:w-32 md:w-48 z-20"
      />

      <img src="/images/star.png" alt="Logo" class="w-16 sm:w-20 md:w-24 z-20" />
    </div>
    <h1
      class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight uppercase tracking-tight italic"
    >
      <span class="text-[#E1629F] block">Abriendo alas donde otros</span>
      <span class="text-[#2B3A8C] block">construyeron cadenas</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-6 text-gray-700 text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
      En Libera México trabajamos para <strong
        >proteger, acompañar y reconstruir</strong
      > la vida de niñas, niños y adolescentes sobrevivientes de trata y violencia
      sexual.
    </p>

    <button
      class="mt-8 bg-[#E1629F] hover:bg-[#c94d8a] text-white font-semibold py-3 sm:py-4 px-8 sm:px-10 rounded-full text-sm sm:text-lg transition-all transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg uppercase tracking-wider"
    >
      Sé un constructor de sueños
    </button>
  </div>
</section>
